lyrics to Baudelaire's poetry.</i>

01:34.402 --> 01:39.040
<i>By 1973, Micky Adams
had won eleven Grammys.</i>

01:39.173 --> 01:43.844
<i>By 1974, he had sold over
70 million records.</i>

01:43.977 --> 01:49.115
<i>And by 1975, he was
off-the-grid: a ghost.</i>

01:49.248 --> 01:50.884
