"When opportunity knocks,

05:13.653 --> 05:14.987
don't be too stoned
to answer."

05:15.122 --> 05:18.391
Dylan never said that,
but if he was here right now,

05:18.524 --> 05:20.527
I bet he'd say, "Fuck off!"

05:20.661 --> 05:22.329
<i>One day,
and I hope it's soon,</i>

05:22.461 --> 05:24.798
<i>I'm going to smash
a pie in this kid's face.</i>

05:24.930 --> 05:27.367
Three of you
are really good.

05:31.771 --> 05:34.408
Hey! Um, sorry
about that.

05:34.540 --> 05:37.911
