10:53.961 --> 10:55.995
<i>♪ Oh, let's cruise
Up to the city, shoot ♪</i>

10:56.129 --> 11:01.100
<i>♪ I've got nothin' to lose
But my brown suede boots ♪</i>

11:03.001 --> 11:06.038
<i>♪ There's no two ways
About this town ♪</i>

11:06.172 --> 11:09.743
<i>♪ There's only one road out
And that's down ♪</i>

11:14.248 --> 11:15.715
Talk to me.

11:15.849 --> 11:18.752
- Guess I shouldn't be shocked.
- <i>By?</i>

11:18.885 --> 11:20.552
<i>The fact that a
record guy lied to me.</i>

11:20.687 --> 11:23.823
Not that you're even
a record guy in the first place.

11:23.956 --> 11:26.558
- Uh-oh.
- <i>How are things in the mail room?</i>

11:26.692 --> 11:27.826
Busted.

11:27.961 --> 11:31.731
- So busted.
- Things in the mail room are temporary.

11:34.033 --> 11:35.269
Fuck!

12:00.561 --> 12:04.798
<i>♪ The wind is cold
On my face ♪</i>

12:06.365 --> 12:09.901
<i>♪ I feel the chill
Of the ocean spray ♪</i>

12:10.035 --> 12:14.306
<i>♪ Right where I belong
They think they know it all ♪</i>

12:14.440 --> 12:17.076
<i>♪ God give 'em peace ♪</i>

12:17.210 --> 12:21.047
<i>♪ They think they know
What's right for me ♪</i>

12:21.181 --> 12:23.283
<i>♪ I'm high above the clouds ♪</i>

12:23.416 --> 12:27.854
<i>♪ Little do they know ♪</i>

12:27.986 --> 12:34.127
<i>♪ Man, they just
