26:19.684 --> 26:22.120
Follow-through is
the street where I live.

26:22.253 --> 26:23.288
That's a pretty
boring street.

26:23.422 --> 26:25.257
You must be
the daughter.

26:25.391 --> 26:27.793
According to
the father.

26:27.925 --> 26:28.894
I'm Charlie.

26:29.027 --> 26:31.063
