26:31.195 --> 26:32.631
Huh, like the song.

26:32.765 --> 26:34.932
Nope, not about me.

26:35.067 --> 26:36.634
Is your dad home?

26:36.769 --> 26:37.970
He's asleep.

26:38.103 --> 26:40.707
- Can you wake him up?
- I can, but I won't.

26:40.839 --> 26:45.544
Your old man laced my drink
with God-knows-what,

26:45.678 --> 26:46.979
and I woke up naked.

26:47.113 --> 26:50.283
My head is on fire, and I think
I might spontaneously combust.

26:50.415 --> 26:51.716
You're gonna need
to relax.

26:51.849 --> 26:54.653
I'm in no mood for
this early morning badinage.

26:54.787 --> 26:56.087
Ooh, badinage,
good word.

26:56.221 --> 26:58.391
I bet you might
even know what it means.

26:59.625 --> 27:01.059
I'll be back.

27:02.127 --> 27:04.163
You think he's crazy,
don't you?

27:04.296 --> 27:07.599
Yeah. Don't you?

27:07.732 --> 27:10.101
You left here yesterday
saying you were out of here

27:10.236 --> 27:11.436
'cause he's out of his skull.

27:11.569 --> 27:13.771
He's not crazy.
He's just hiding.

27:13.905 --> 27:15.140
From?

27:16.275 --> 27:18.344
All those
other people.

27:22.382 --> 27:23.416
Fuck!

27:37.863 --> 27:40.866
So, he signed it?

27:41.000 --> 27:43.669
Yeah,
I dropped it off at legal.

27:43.801 --> 27:46.238
<i>I figure this
buys me about a week.</i>

27:46.372 --> 27:48.274
My bible is short
and fat-free.

27:48.406 --> 27:51.042
When I say I'm gonna
do something, I do it.

27:51.176 --> 27:52.176
Old school, baby.

27:52.310 --> 27:54.712
Yeah, that's right.

27:57.048 --> 28:00.786
I used to think maybe
I didn't deserve all this,

28:00.920 --> 28:02.321
but I snapped
out of it.

28:02.454 --> 28:07.025
This is America, Pilgrim.
You get what you deserve.

28:07.159 --> 28:08.394
He signed it.

28:09.862 --> 28:11.130
Follow me.

28:13.199 --> 28:14.734
<i>I will follow him.</i>

28:16.601 --> 28:19.238
